{
  "texts": [
    "The deep network used is GRU 34, a type of LSTM return network.",
    "One of the advantages of this work is the use of the K-nearest neighbor method to train the model, the accuracy of which is guaranteed.",
    "Second, it can recommend new items whose similarities cannot be calculated.",
    "Third, it dramatically reduces system performance, which benefits the actual applications of recommenders.",
    "In [54], an advanced recommendation method called AROLS has been proposed."
  ]
}